## For Commercial Use

**Commercial use of this software requires a separate commercial license.**

### What Requires a Commercial License?

A commercial license is required if you:

- Use the software in any business, company, or organization
- Use the software to provide services to customers or clients
- Integrate the software into a commercial product or service
- Deploy the software on infrastructure used for business purposes
- Use the software in government or educational institutions in an official capacity
- Redistribute the software as part of a commercial offering
- Use the software to generate revenue directly or indirectly

### Obtaining a Commercial License

To obtain a commercial license, please contact:

**Email**: aezi.zhu@icloud.com  
**Subject**: g Commercial License Request

Please include in your inquiry:
- Your organization name and size
- Intended use case
- Number of deployments/users
- Any specific requirements or questions

We offer flexible licensing options for:
- Small businesses and startups
- Enterprise deployments
- OEM/redistribution
- Custom development and support

### Commercial License Benefits

Commercial licenses include:
- Legal right to use in commercial environments
- Priority support
- Service level agreements (SLA) available
- Custom feature development options
- Indemnification options
- Volume discounts for large deployments

